{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make all workplace bullying illegal",
        "additional_details": "There is no law to specifically protect people from workplace bullying, and we believe some companies turn a blind eye to bullying, or even condone this.\r\n \r\nSome organisations have reported that around 1 in 3 workers are the victim of workplace bullying. Many workers may feel stuck in a role where they are bullied, because they are financially dependant on their job.\r\n \r\nBullying can be hugely detrimental to victims, and we believe current protections are too limited.\r\n",
        "background": "We want the Government to change the law to make all workplace bullying illegal.",
